      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection must be justified with sensitivity analysis; hemolysis constitutive model must be validated against blood damage data at relevant shear stress magnitudes and exposure times.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected without sensitivity study against alternative models. Power-law hemolysis model parameters were taken from literature without re-calibration to current blood source. Model form uncertainty is unquantified. Achieved level 2 is critically below required level 5."
