      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on 4 of 12 identified uncertain inputs. Blood viscosity, RBC fragility index, and surface roughness were treated as deterministic. Dominant input sensitivity not formally ranked. Achieved level 2 is below required level 4."
